                                <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> der elter und
                            <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> der jünger, die Speger,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz ir etwievil gelts ynnenhabt, daran
                        sie teil <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz
                        ir <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan>, <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> irenteil
